{"tid":172183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔識裝燈]唔該電工jj入嚟","createTime":"2017-03-25T18:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T20:30:38.000Z","uid":56961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7fdcdc136a293267a149889bac5e38038d46c9a","tid":172183,"uid":56961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:09:53.000Z","msg":"係ikea買咗揀天花燈唔識裝 佢有分 L N 線 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/26/020227_c8a740b7c9582250078077ba3f3f585a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F26%2F020227_c8a740b7c9582250078077ba3f3f585a.jpg&h=5f28128e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係我本身盞燈佢有3條黑線同1條藍線 上網睇話09年後條藍線由L線變N線 咁我個3條黑線係L定N?<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1Ud2zu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1Ud2zu.jpg&h=283e0072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋係咪要駁晒3條黑線定1條已經夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b50a3546c418a61ce1a275e7d99a9352100b9be","tid":172183,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:14:13.000Z","msg":"藍L黑N<br />\n3條一齊"},{"pid":"c9342613d1603683b2d35eca1a2bde3915d89fe3","tid":172183,"uid":56961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藍L黑N<br />\n3條一齊</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打 但係ikea個制每邊得2個窿 點插晒3條黑線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/26/022705_5aa966a8760be6d1a76121f0b58496c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2